Lunar rocks (Stalagmites in game) are rare rocks that can only be mined by players with 60 Mining during the Lunar Diplomacy quest or the Fremennik Exiles quest. Lunar ore is mined at the stalagmites in the western part of the dungeon in north-east Lunar Isle. It can be smelted into a lunar bar through the Smithing skill and then made into a lunar helm. Other than that, the ore has no other use.
